NK126(cho)003:1: // bod kyi bla ma rnams kyi dgongs nyams kyi lo rgyus bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)003:2: dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)003:3: da ni bod kyi bla ma rnams kyi dgongs nyams kyi lo rgyus 'byung ste /
NK126(cho)003:4: de nas rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra ni /
NK126(cho)003:5: yul dbus kyi yar lung pa /
NK126(cho)003:6: yab rnyag srag ra lha snang dang /
NK126(cho)003:7: yum sru za rgyal mo skyes kyi sras /
NK126(cho)003:8: mi chos kyi ming rgyal srid blo gros /
NK126(cho)003:9: chos ming rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK126(cho)003:10: gsang ba'i mtshan dri med zla shar zhes bya ba /
NK126(cho)003:11: sa drug pa'i byang chub sems dpa' lkog ma dang /
NK126(cho)003:12: snying kha na rdo rje rgya gram yod pa yin no //
NK126(cho)003:13: der rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra'i thugs la /
NK126(cho)003:14: nga slob dpon chen po b+hi ma la mi tra'i lo ts+aa ba byas nas /
NK126(cho)003:15: bi ma la mi tra'i thugs la mkhyen tshad ngas shes snyam mo //
NK126(cho)003:16: nga slob dpon g.yu sgra snying po'i lo ts+aa ba
NK126(cho)003:17: byas nas slob dpon g.yu sgra snying pos mkhyen tshad
NK126(cho)003:19: slob dpon gnyis pos chos phyogs rer las mi shes /
NK126(cho)003:20: ngas chos gnyis ka la chos bslab pas /
NK126(cho)003:21: gnyis ka bas ngas mkhas snyams pa'i blo cig skyes pa la /
NK126(cho)003:22: bi ma la mi tra'i thugs la /
NK126(cho)003:23: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ka ma ra 'di /
NK126(cho)003:24: rloms sems gcig skyes dgongs te /
NK126(cho)003:25: bi ma la mi tra'i zhal nas /
NK126(cho)003:26: ku ma ra yar rtsang skyi rtsang 'dus pa'i chu
NK126(cho)003:27: la bum pa 'di'i gang khyer la shog gsungs pas
NK126(cho)003:28: / ku ma ras yar gtsang spyi gtsang 'dus pa'i chu la bum pa gang bcus ste /
NK126(cho)003:29: bi ma la'i phyag tu phul nas /
NK126(cho)003:31: ku ma ra lag mthil zed dang gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:32: ku ma ras lag mthil zed pas /
NK126(cho)003:33: bum pa'i mchu nas mar chu thig pa cig btig pas /
NK126(cho)003:34: ku ma ra de go'am gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:35: de ma go ci ltar lags zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:37: rgya gar gyi yul na chos yar rtsang spyi rtsang 'dus pa'i chu bo chen po tsam yong /
NK126(cho)003:38: de la nged gnyis kyi bum pa gang gi tshad re shes /
NK126(cho)003:39: de la khyod kyi thig pa gcig tsam shes pa ngas bslab pa yin /
NK126(cho)003:40: de la khyod rloms sems ma che gcig gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:41: yang bi ma la'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:42: ston pa'i bka' ni nam mkha'i mtha' dang 'dra //
NK126(cho)003:43: rgya gar yul nas chu bo chen po tsam //
NK126(cho)003:44: mkhas pa gnyis kyi bum pa gang do tsam //
NK126(cho)003:45: ku ma ra la thig pa gcig gnyis tsam //
NK126(cho)003:46: khyod la de las med do nga rgyal ma che cig gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:47: der b+aee ro ts+aa na rgya bod gnyis na mkhas par grags nas /
NK126(cho)003:48: yang rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras /
NK126(cho)003:49: sems phyogs tha dag gi man ngag /
NK126(cho)003:50: snyan rgyud du dri ba zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:51: b+aee ro tsa na'i thugs la /
NK126(cho)003:52: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra 'di mkhas pa snod dang ldan pa yin par thugs la dgongs nas /
NK126(cho)003:53: man ngag thams cad kyi bcud ku ma ra la gtig go //
NK126(cho)003:54: der rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra'i thugs la /
NK126(cho)003:55: 'di 'dra'i gdams ngag gi snod mkhas pa bi ma
NK126(cho)003:56: la dang g.yu sgra gnyis la yang med snyams pa'i
NK126(cho)003:58: des shes bya'i sgrib par gyur nas /
NK126(cho)003:59: brtson du lan gsum du shor te rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra'i pha spun po /
NK126(cho)003:60: rnyag khar 'bo ras bor 'phrog byas nas /
NK126(cho)003:61: blon ngas ngom stag ra klu gang gi mi bsad pa'i mi sha 'ong bas /
NK126(cho)003:62: lag tu song gi dog nas btsun pa'i chas su zhug te /
NK126(cho)003:64: mgar ba beg rtse'i mgar tshangs su gzim na /
NK126(cho)003:65: mgar ba de mgo bo rgya mdud 'drar 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:72: lus khro bo'i cha lugs 'dra bar 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:73: rkang lag bya sder 'dra bar 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:74: brtul zhugs glang chen 'dra bar 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:75: 'gros bya ngang pa'i srabs 'dra bar 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:76: yan lag 'phrul du 'dug pa mtshan rtags bcu gnyis tshang ba gcig 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:77: snod du rung ram mi rung brtags pa'i phyir /
NK126(cho)003:78: mgar ba la khab cig slang byas pas byin /
NK126(cho)003:79: nang par kha mig phul nas /
NK126(cho)003:82: de ltar nang ma gsum byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:84: kha mig 'phro 'phror phug kyin byin pas /
NK126(cho)003:86: 'gar ba ngas sdud pa 'bud dam byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:87: bus zer nas sbud pa 'bud cing /
NK126(cho)003:88: nyan thos kyi tshig shar tho re btang bas /
NK126(cho)003:89: de skad ma zer bar spud pa bus zer ro //
NK126(cho)003:90: de nas byang chub sems dpa'i tshig bshad re btang bas /
NK126(cho)003:91: da ci bas ku co chung ngu song ste /
NK126(cho)003:92: sbud pa bud tsam las mi zer ro //
NK126(cho)003:93: de nas rdzogs chen gyi gdams pa btang bas /
NK126(cho)003:94: brdung bshol nas nyan gyis 'dug pas /
NK126(cho)003:95: de nas rgya'i 'dra 'bag chen mo thugs la mnos nas gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)003:96: sbud pa shol la thon zer nas /
NK126(cho)003:97: tho ba skyur nas nyan kyin 'dug go //
NK126(cho)003:98: sems phyogs mtha' dag thugs la bton pas /
NK126(cho)003:99: mgar ba beg rtses res bzo byed /
NK126(cho)003:100: res bzo mi byed par 'dug pas /
NK126(cho)003:101: slob dpon gyi rgya'i 'dra 'bags chen mo thugs la gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:102: mgar ba beg rtses lag cha rkyang ste bskyur nas /
NK126(cho)003:105: mgar ba snyan pa zhig byung ngam byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:108: bdag la chos zhig zhu byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:110: nga sang nas log nas 'ong gi gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:111: mgar nas slob dpon la do nub bzhugs 'tshal zhes zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:113: der slob dpon gyis nub mo'i rnal lam na /
NK126(cho)003:114: mgar ba beg rtses gser gyis bum pa thogs nas 'dug gin rmis /
NK126(cho)003:115: slob dpon la bdud rtsi bum pa gang 'dug gin rmis /
NK126(cho)003:116: slob dpon gyi bum pa gang po de dang mgar ba'i gser gyis bum par byon gyin rmis nas /
NK126(cho)003:118: mdangs mtshan ltas rnal lam bzang bas mgar ba khyod snod ldan du 'ong bar 'dug pas /
NK126(cho)003:119: ngas chos sbyin par zhal gyis bzhes so //
NK126(cho)003:121: tshe la nges pa med pas /
NK126(cho)003:122: da lta rang zhu 'tshal zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:123: der slob dpon gyis dbang rdzogs par bskur nas /
NK126(cho)003:125: de nas slob dpon rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma rang yul byon pa la /
NK126(cho)003:126: slob dpon ngam stag ra klu gang gis mi sha
NK126(cho)003:127: yod pas ngam stag ra klu gang gi lag tu
NK126(cho)003:129: slob dpon mkhar dape'u sum thog yod pa'i bar khang du gdos lcags sbrag mas bsdom /
NK126(cho)003:130: brtson rdzi gnyis kyis g.yas g.yon nas bsrungs nas yod pa la /
NK126(cho)003:132: slob dpon brtson du bzung ba thos nas /
NK126(cho)003:133: shin tu yid mya ngan gyi gdung pas zin ste /
NK126(cho)003:139: nang nub lto ma tshud do //
NK126(cho)003:140: de nas mgar ba beg rtses /
NK126(cho)003:143: blon po ngam stag ra klu gong gi mkhar la phug pas /
NK126(cho)003:144: ra ba nas bar khang du ma thar te /
NK126(cho)003:145: de'i dus su yang log go //
NK126(cho)003:147: ngam stag ra klu gong gis mkhar la 'dzeg pas /
NK126(cho)003:148: khang thog nas bar khang du ma thar nas /
NK126(cho)003:149: lcags ngar la thag pa btags nas bar khang du btang te /
NK126(cho)003:150: bar khang gis tshad blangs nas kyang de dus log go //
NK126(cho)003:151: yang mgar bas lcags sna mi mthun pa stong la khab mkhan gyi ras mas brdul /
NK126(cho)003:153: shing gis nag kyis mes bsreg ste bzhus nas /
NK126(cho)003:154: de la gcod gri zhing la khyud gang /
NK126(cho)003:155: ring thung gru gang brdungs te /
NK126(cho)003:156: ngar tshad dang ldan par byas nas /
NK126(cho)003:157: rdo yang chod pa'i ngar btang ste khyer /
NK126(cho)003:158: skas gdang bu nyi shu rtsa cig pa gcig khyer /
NK126(cho)003:159: rog po gnyis kho rang dang gsum gyis /
NK126(cho)003:160: ngam stag ra klu gang gi mkhar dape'u la /
NK126(cho)003:161: rked phug byas nas nang du phyin nas /
NK126(cho)003:162: brtson rdzi gnyis sngur pa ngur ngur 'dug nas /
NK126(cho)003:163: mgar bas slob dpon slob dpon byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:166: nga gdos lcags sbrag ma yod gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:168: brtson rdzi gnyis kyi ske la gcod gri re re brgyab pas /
NK126(cho)003:169: ske ni skad med du rbad rbad song /
NK126(cho)003:170: de nas brtson rdzi gnyis kyi rkang pa la gcod gri re re brgyab pas /
NK126(cho)003:171: tshig khams gdub bu rbad rbad bcad do //
NK126(cho)003:172: de nas slob dpon gdos lcags bkrol nas slob dpon
NK126(cho)003:173: mgar bas khur nas skas la bab pas thar ro
NK126(cho)003:174: // der slob dpon gdos lcags kyi theb nas gshegs pa ma byung ba las /
NK126(cho)003:175: mgar ba ber brtses slob dpon khur nas bros pas /
NK126(cho)003:176: slob dpon dgyes te slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK126(cho)003:177: snod byo snod byo snod byo gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:178: slob dpon gyi thugs la mkhyen tshad chu dong nas
NK126(cho)003:179: dong du chu byos pa bzhin du mgar bas shes
NK126(cho)003:180: so // de ni mos gus kyi rtsol bsgrub drag po byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:181: las dang sgrib pa dag par byas nas /
NK126(cho)003:183: de nas mgar ba'i chung ma sa tsa khyer rgod na re /
NK126(cho)003:184: slob dpon mi ma yin gyi skyobs par gyur pa la /
NK126(cho)003:186: brtson du 'chor bar mchis pa la ci lags zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:188: ngas bla ma mkhas pa gsum la chos zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:189: da nga mkhas pa cig dang mnyam mo bsam pas /
NK126(cho)003:190: de shes bya'i sgrib par 'gyur ba yin /
NK126(cho)003:191: rang sems skye med rtogs pas /
NK126(cho)003:192: phyi ma la smin rgyu med pa min gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:193: lha dpal gyi ye shes la /
NK126(cho)003:194: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi chos 'chad kyi yod pa la /
NK126(cho)003:195: slob dpon rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra 'o yug tu bzhud pa la /
NK126(cho)003:196: 'o yug gi gnas pos btson du bzung ste /
NK126(cho)003:197: chos log mkhan yin zer nas dngos su bsgyur ro //
NK126(cho)003:198: des sog po lha dpal ye shes kyi thos nas /
NK126(cho)003:199: skra thog thog brag nas dug po gcig gyon /
NK126(cho)003:200: dig par bcos nas gnas su yan blongs kyin bsdad pas lags khong na re /
NK126(cho)003:201: khyod kyi ming ci yin bris pas /
NK126(cho)003:203: lags stabs ling ling las mid nas /
NK126(cho)003:205: dug po ni hrul nas snang /
NK126(cho)003:206: sprang hrul po btag nas yod pa la dus nam zhig tsa na /
NK126(cho)003:207: btsun pa rang la chos ston song ba'i bar la /
NK126(cho)003:211: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga bshad cing yod pa la /
NK126(cho)003:212: ru mdo na bzhugs kyin yod pa la /
NK126(cho)003:213: ru gnya' na ku tsi ring ring gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)003:214: lha dpal gyis ye shes kyis /
NK126(cho)003:216: sbrul chen po zhig gi ru'i mgul na bkris nas 'dug pa sbrul gyi mgo nas mar zos pas /
NK126(cho)003:217: phyed tsam zad tsa na ru rgyal nas 'dug pa de /
NK126(cho)003:218: song nas ci yin gsungs ste /
NK126(cho)003:220: ru'i mgul pa nas sbrul gyi dkris nas gda' bas /
NK126(cho)003:221: de la bdag gi sbrul mgo nas mar zos pas /
NK126(cho)003:223: ru rgyal song pas lags byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:224: de ltar thugs lan gsum gnyis so //
NK126(cho)003:225: de nas slob dpon gyis mgar ba beg rtses la dbang mchog bco brgyad bskur nas /
NK126(cho)003:226: bka' rgyud lung gsum man ngag gi bcud gtigs nas
NK126(cho)003:227: mtshan kyang sog po lha dpal gyis ye shes bya
NK126(cho)003:228: bar btags so // de nas slob dpon rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras /
NK126(cho)003:229: dgongs pa'i nyams zhal nas gsungs pa 'di skad do //
NK126(cho)003:230: a ti rang gis sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)003:231: brtsal bas ci rnyed mkha' ltar dag /
NK126(cho)003:232: bzhag pas mi sdod mkha' ltar 'char //
NK126(cho)003:233: rgyu 'bras ma grub ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)003:234: rtsol zhing bsgrub pa'i nad dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:235: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK126(cho)003:236: sangs rgyas zhes su brtags pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:239: gzhi la 'khrul pa ma rig med //
NK126(cho)003:240: thams cad byang chub sems su gsal //
NK126(cho)003:241: de phyir dug lnga byang chub sems yin pas //
NK126(cho)003:242: spang du med pa yid ches bya //
NK126(cho)003:245: a ti rang gi sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)003:246: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK126(cho)003:247: gdod nas ma skyes mnyams pa nyid //
NK126(cho)003:248: ye shes lhun grub chen po yin //
NK126(cho)003:250: de bas na chos dang chos min bya ba gnyis
NK126(cho)003:251: med lta ba dang lta byed bya ba gnyis med
NK126(cho)003:252: / bsgom bya dang bsgom byed bya ba gnyis med /
NK126(cho)003:253: sangs rgyas pa dang ma rgyas pa bya ba gnyis med /
NK126(cho)003:254: de ni chos nyid mnyams pa nyid kyis sangs rgyas bya ba yin no //
NK126(cho)003:255: zhes sog po lha dpal gyis ye shes la rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras gdams pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:256: sog po lha dpal ye shes kyis /
NK126(cho)003:257: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra la gser srang sum cu so drug phul nas /
NK126(cho)003:258: rkyang phyag lan stong du btsal lo //
NK126(cho)003:260: rnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra'i sog po lha dpal
NK126(cho)003:261: gyi ye shes la rdzogs pa chen po'i don gsungs
NK126(cho)003:263: de nas yang sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes kyis /
NK126(cho)003:265: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings su gda' //
NK126(cho)003:266: 'khor 'das thams cad chos kyi dbyings su gda' //
NK126(cho)003:267: snang srid 'khor 'das chos kyi klong du gda' //
NK126(cho)003:268: 'di la su zhig yid ma ches //
NK126(cho)003:269: thar pa bde ba'i mun nag yin //
NK126(cho)003:270: bdag 'dra mgar ba dpal gyi ye shes kyis //
NK126(cho)003:271: rtsol med sems kyi me long 'dir //
NK126(cho)003:272: gcar gyi nyal bas las rnams zin //
NK126(cho)003:274: de nas yang mgar ba'i chung ma sa tsa khyed rgod na re /
NK126(cho)003:275: mgar ba khyod la mi'i ske bcad pa'i sgrib pas mi sgrib bam byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:276: sog po dpal gyi ye shes na re /
NK126(cho)003:277: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK126(cho)003:278: srog med srog kyang bcad du med //
NK126(cho)003:279: srog kyang skyes bu'i log rtogs tsam zer bas mngon /
NK126(cho)003:280: nga ni skal pa grangs med 'khor ba yin //
NK126(cho)003:281: sdug bsngal las grol bar byed pa yi //
NK126(cho)003:282: bla ma nor bu rin chen lta bu'i sku dgra 'di //
NK126(cho)003:283: the tshom med pa'i sems kyi bsgral gyur na //
NK126(cho)003:284: the tshom med par 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar 'gyur //
NK126(cho)003:285: ces glang po che rabs 'bog kyi rgyud nas gsungs pas mngon //
NK126(cho)003:288: 'o na las rgyu 'bras mi bden nam byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:289: sog po dpal gyi ye shes na re /
NK126(cho)003:290: skye med mkha' ltar dag pa'i sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:291: las yang med la rnam smin med //
NK126(cho)003:292: ci ste rang byung ye shes yin //
NK126(cho)003:293: mtshon du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:294: sgrib pa med par skrag pa med //
NK126(cho)003:296: yang mgar ba mo na re /
NK126(cho)003:297: sgrib pa med ces byas pas ma gol lam zhes byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:298: sog po dpal gyi ye shes na re /
NK126(cho)003:299: a ti sems nyid rtogs pa yis /
NK126(cho)003:300: dge sdig yid la mi byed gol sgrib med //
NK126(cho)003:301: byung tshor rjes su ma 'brang pas //
NK126(cho)003:302: 'jig rten phal par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:303: yod med yul du ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:304: rtag chad mthar ni nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:305: shes rab zab mo'i don gzigs pas //
NK126(cho)003:306: lung du ma bstan nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:307: zhi gnas ro la ma chags pas //
NK126(cho)003:308: bsam gtan bzhi por nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:309: sgo lnga'i rnam shes ma bkags pas //
NK126(cho)003:310: 'du shes med par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:311: rnam rtog ma spang ye grol bas //
NK126(cho)003:312: nyan thos 'gogs par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:313: 'dzin rtog bkar pa'i stong bsgom ma byas pas //
NK126(cho)003:314: rang sangs rgyas su nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:315: rang rig gsal ba phyogs cig ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:316: sems tsam bar ni nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:317: mtshan ma stong par ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:318: dbu ma gnyis su nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:319: thabs kyi bde ba ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:320: chags pa'i lam du nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:321: rgyu 'bras chos la ma ltos pas //
NK126(cho)003:322: 'dus byas chos su nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:323: dge sdig re dogs rtsol med pas //
NK126(cho)003:324: las kyi dbang du nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:325: sems la bden pa'i yul med pas //
NK126(cho)003:326: 'phra ba'i lam du nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:327: lam lnga rim gyis ma sbyangs pas //
NK126(cho)003:328: sa lam bsgrod par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:329: dag pa'i lha ni ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:330: kri ya'i theg par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:331: lta spyod gnyis su ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:332: u pa ya ni nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:333: byang chub sems lnga ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:334: yo ga'i theg par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:335: rnam rtog gnas 'gyur ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:336: ma h+aa yo gar nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:337: dmigs su med 'jog yid med pas //
NK126(cho)003:338: a nu yo gar nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:339: sems nyid mtshon du med pa yi //
NK126(cho)003:340: mtshan ma'i chos su nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:341: phyi nang brtul shugs ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:342: blang dor spyod par nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:343: gnyis med don la ma bsgom pas //
NK126(cho)003:344: mtha' zhan lta bar nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:345: sems nyid la ni mi rtsol bas //
NK126(cho)003:346: mnyams pa nyid la nga mi gol //
NK126(cho)003:347: bya ba med pa'i don rtogs pas //
NK126(cho)003:348: sgrib pa rnam bzhi nga la med //
NK126(cho)003:349: snang ba mi 'gags rang byung la //
NK126(cho)003:350: zhen pa med pa'i ye shes yin //
NK126(cho)003:351: chos nyid 'bras bu ye rdzogs pas //
NK126(cho)003:352: re dogs gnyis bral blang dor med //
NK126(cho)003:353: sa med sa bcu ma bsgrod cig /
NK126(cho)003:354: lam med lam lnga ma bsgrod cig /
NK126(cho)003:355: sgrib med sgrib gnyis ma sbyangs cig /
NK126(cho)003:356: tshogs med tshogs gnyis ma bsags cig /
NK126(cho)003:357: rdo rje 'dzin dang stug po bkod //
NK126(cho)003:358: rdo rje 'chang dang kun tu bzang //
NK126(cho)003:359: thig le nyag cig don rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)003:360: ci bzhin pa nyid sa mchog ste //
NK126(cho)003:361: rim par bgrod du ga la yod //
NK126(cho)003:362: chos kun rang bzhin med pa nyid //
NK126(cho)003:363: mya ngan 'das zhes de la bya //
NK126(cho)003:366: khyod la de lta bu'i gdams pa 'dog na /
NK126(cho)003:367: bdag la shi brgyag cig mdzub tshugs su zhu byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:368: sog po dpal gyi ye shes na re 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:369: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK126(cho)003:370: su yi mkhas kyang bcos su med //
NK126(cho)003:371: re dogs mtshams med lnga yis sdig pas kyang //
NK126(cho)003:372: sems nyid dngos po'i mtshan mar 'gro mi srid //
NK126(cho)003:373: bskal pa'i bsgom bsgrub 'bad rtsol gyis //
NK126(cho)003:374: sems nyid mtshan ma'i dngos por grol mi srid //
NK126(cho)003:375: ci phyir mkha' ltar dag pa'i phyir //
NK126(cho)003:376: rang gis gzung 'dzin re dogs 'khrul pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:377: srin bu kha chus gtum pa 'dra //
NK126(cho)003:378: re dogs med par mnyams pa'i don la 'dug /
NK126(cho)003:381: ngan song gis gnas bya ba ru rang dbang med
NK126(cho)003:382: par las kyi rlung bya bas khyer nas 'gro zer
NK126(cho)003:383: na / de bden nam mi bden lags byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:384: yang lha dpal gyi ye shes na re 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:387: rang sems 'khrul pa la zer ba yin /
NK126(cho)003:388: rang gi rang rlung la ma bskur ba las /
NK126(cho)003:389: gzhan du yang ngan song la khrid mkhan med /
NK126(cho)003:399: snang ba sna tshogs su dran pas /
NK126(cho)003:400: wa la la rgyas pa la /
NK126(cho)003:403: bya ba sus kyang ma shes /
NK126(cho)003:406: mi mthong ba 'di ka rang sangs rgyas yin gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:408: dmyal srung bya ba gcig gis rang dbang med par khrid nas ngan song du 'gro zer nas /
NK126(cho)003:411: yang lha dpal gyi ye shes na re 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:412: skye med mkha' ltar dag pa'i sems nyid las //
NK126(cho)003:413: sus kyang ma mthong mthong ba med par bsgrib tu med //
NK126(cho)003:414: brdung brtsogs dang brtso bsreg gang la byed //
NK126(cho)003:415: 'khor 'das thams cad rang sems skye med du ma rtogs pas len /
NK126(cho)003:416: mgar mo skye med sems la ltos la /
NK126(cho)003:417: blo la rtsol bsgrub med par zhog /
NK126(cho)003:418: ces gdams pas sa tsa khyo rgod kyang skye med kyi don rtogs nas /
NK126(cho)003:419: phyir mi ldog par sangs rgyas so //
NK126(cho)003:421: sog po lha dpal gyi sems kyi rtogs pa'i nyams bshad pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:422: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che ni /
NK126(cho)003:424: yab gnub lha bzang legs pa dang /
NK126(cho)003:427: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che bya ba'i rgyu mtshan kyang /
NK126(cho)003:428: dang po bal po ba su d+ha ra la chos gsan du gshegs pa'i dus su lam khar /
NK126(cho)003:429: nam mkha' la phyag na rdo rje'i sku /
NK126(cho)003:430: mi ring sngon po gcig tu bstan nas /
NK126(cho)003:431: khyod kyi rus pa ni gnub yin /
NK126(cho)003:433: dgongs pa ni sangs rgyas dang mnyams /
NK126(cho)003:434: sems can gyi don yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che ltar mdzad pas /
NK126(cho)003:435: khyod kyi ming ni gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che bya bar thog shig /
NK126(cho)003:436: gsungs nas phyag tu gser gyi rdo rje gcig gtad do //
NK126(cho)003:437: de lta bu'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK126(cho)003:438: che lta bu sa bzhi pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK126(cho)003:439: des / rtogs pa'i don gsungs pa 'di lta ste /
NK126(cho)003:440: sems can ma rig nad gdung gsal ba'i phyir //
NK126(cho)003:441: chos rnams ngo bo gcig tu bstan pa'i don //
NK126(cho)003:442: sngon tshe gang nas bsgrub pa'i las can la //
NK126(cho)003:443: rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi don 'di ltar bshad par bya //
NK126(cho)003:445: lta bsgom spyod 'bras bzhi po don gcig ste /
NK126(cho)003:446: dper na gleng gzhi gling phran gzha' tshon kun //
NK126(cho)003:447: dbyibs dang kha dog mi 'dra sna tshogs kyang //
NK126(cho)003:448: nam mkha'i ngang du ro gcig bye brag med //
NK126(cho)003:449: de bzhin lta bsgom spyod 'bras la sogs ni //
NK126(cho)003:450: tha snyad ci rnyed spros kyang ngo bo gcig las med //
NK126(cho)003:451: de nyid rang sems nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK126(cho)003:452: de phyir bdag gi chos rnams rang rig nyid du rtogs //
NK126(cho)003:453: gcig las mi 'gal nges pa'i don //
NK126(cho)003:454: yod med dbu ma'i sgro bskur med pa ni //
NK126(cho)003:455: sems nyid rang byung ye shes don ston pas //
NK126(cho)003:456: ci spyad byang chub sems kyi ngang du gsal //
NK126(cho)003:457: gsal tsam nyid na zhan chags gang yang med //
NK126(cho)003:458: dper na nam mkha' rlung po gang la chags med ltar //
NK126(cho)003:459: rnal 'byor 'khor 'das gnyis la chags pa med pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:460: de phyir thog ma med nas rang sems ye nas chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)003:461: 'gro don rnam snang ci spyod khyad par can gyi don dam kun bzang nyid //
NK126(cho)003:462: dbyer med lhun grub chen po'i sku //
NK126(cho)003:463: phrin las rnam bzhi dgag bsgrub med pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:465: yang gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches /
NK126(cho)003:466: theg pa 'og ma zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir lta ba'i gyad tshig bcu pa 'di ltar gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:467: stag mo kha gdong gi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:468: khams gsum zas kyi nga mi 'drang //
NK126(cho)003:469: lhag ma med par zos pas da lta lto bde tsam //
NK126(cho)003:470: da ni lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:472: ri rgyal rtse nas gnon pa'i dgongs pa //
NK126(cho)003:473: sa lam bsgrod pas nga yis sar ma phyin //
NK126(cho)003:474: ma bsgrod gam pa gang gi srid gsum gnon //
NK126(cho)003:475: de ni gang nas gang du tshangs pa'i lam //
NK126(cho)003:476: bya bral chos dang mthun pa la //
NK126(cho)003:477: lam med lam du zhugs pa'i nad che ba'o //
NK126(cho)003:478: zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po sa gcig pa'i don +thii /
NK126(cho)003:479: chu srin kha gdong kyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:480: mi ro bye ru lto khyur mid 'gro dus med /
NK126(cho)003:481: chu srin kha gdong khyur mid byas pas lto bde tsam /
NK126(cho)003:482: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa'i grangs kyi skye med don ma mthong /
NK126(cho)003:483: a ti rtsol med mthong bas skye ba med pa'i de nyid do //
NK126(cho)003:484: de ni rgyu dang 'bras bu'i ming 'dogs shing /
NK126(cho)003:485: dge sdig gnyis ka rnam par sel /
NK126(cho)003:487: me long g.ya' dag gi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:488: phyi nang yul la ltas pa ngam tshim /
NK126(cho)003:489: phyi nang med par ltas pas dar cig nga yi dbang po tshim /
NK126(cho)003:490: de ni phyi nang gnyis ka med pa'i phyi nyid ni //
NK126(cho)003:492: mkha' la klong yangs kyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:493: sa rdo brtsegs pa'i khang par nga ma shong //
NK126(cho)003:494: kun bzang yangs pa'i khang par da bzod brkyang bskum shong //
NK126(cho)003:495: de ni kun bzang yangs pa chos kyis dbyings //
NK126(cho)003:497: khams gsum yongs sgrol gyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:498: lce'i dbang pos smras pas nga yi gsung ma rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:499: snod bcud sgra skad sna tshogs kyi nga yi gsung yang rdzogs /
NK126(cho)003:500: de ni tshig med tshig dang bral bas rgyal ba'i gsung /
NK126(cho)003:501: de bzhin lce yi dbang pos kyang /
NK126(cho)003:502: de la brjod du rdul tsam med /
NK126(cho)003:504: za 'og ber khyim gyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:505: rin chen sna tshogs kyi brgyan yang de yis nga yis rgyan ma rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:506: phyi nang snang srid bkod pa nga yi rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:507: de ni kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK126(cho)003:508: chos kyi dbyings kyi rgyan ces gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:510: rang byung lhun grub kyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:511: mngon sum rjes dpag nyid kyi gzhal yas 'dir /
NK126(cho)003:513: dmigs pa gsum gyis rig pa'i gzhung bkod de /
NK126(cho)003:514: dgag bsgrub blang dor byas kyang rang sems ma rtogs gol sar ltung /
NK126(cho)003:515: slar la rtsol bsgrub a ti bsgribs te nga rgyal dug lnga rgyas /
NK126(cho)003:516: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma'i mtha' la zin /
NK126(cho)003:517: de ni lam med lam log srid pa'i 'khor bar 'khyams /
NK126(cho)003:518: ci ste lam la bsgrod gyur na //
NK126(cho)003:519: nam mkha'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK126(cho)003:521: mi zad gter chen lta bu'i dgongs pa la //
NK126(cho)003:522: nga ni chos kyi dbang phyug po //
NK126(cho)003:523: med pa zad mi shes pa'i mdzod nang nas //
NK126(cho)003:524: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i gter chen 'chang //
NK126(cho)003:525: de ni bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin las //
NK126(cho)003:526: bza' ba'i thabs la rag pa med //
NK126(cho)003:528: nor bu rdul bral gyi dgongs pa /
NK126(cho)003:529: snang srid chos sku ma bcos pa /
NK126(cho)003:530: ma rtogs snang tshul bcu bdun snang /
NK126(cho)003:531: a nu man chad snang tshul bcu bdun ni /
NK126(cho)003:533: mu stegs rtag chad gnyis kyi lam gnyis /
NK126(cho)003:534: theg pa rim dgu rnams yin no //
NK126(cho)003:535: brgyad kyi ma mthong chos sku rin po che //
NK126(cho)003:536: shin tu rnal 'byor nga yi mthong //
NK126(cho)003:537: de ni ngo mtshar mthong ba ma dmigs ngo mtshar mthong ba'i dmigs //
NK126(cho)003:538: de phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan ces de la bya //
NK126(cho)003:541: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che'i rtogs pa'i don gsungs pa'i skabs ste gsum pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:542: de nas gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che /
NK126(cho)003:543: shel brag na dal bar bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK126(cho)003:544: dus rgyun du gzim nas bzhugs pa la /
NK126(cho)003:545: rgen mo skyo tsha bya ba na re /
NK126(cho)003:546: slob dpon dge sbyor chos spyod mi mdzad par dus
NK126(cho)003:547: rgyun du gzim shing rnal log pa ci lags zhus
NK126(cho)003:548: pas / slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK126(cho)003:549: nga chos nyid kyi klong du gnyid log pa yin gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:550: der rgen mo skyo tshas slob dpon la /
NK126(cho)003:551: 'o na de 'dra'i gdams ngag cig zhu 'tshal zhus pa las /
NK126(cho)003:553: khyod rang gi gdams ngag gi klong na 'dug pa /
NK126(cho)003:554: nga la zhu ci dgos gsungs pas /
NK126(cho)003:556: de ltar bdag gis ma rtogs par lags pas /
NK126(cho)003:557: gdams ngag gcig zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:560: mig gi mig mi mthong ba dang 'dra gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:561: slob dpon gyi thog phab car phog tu rgen mo la gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)003:562: mig gi gzugs mthong ba dang /
NK126(cho)003:565: lus kyi reg bya tshor ba dang /
NK126(cho)003:566: rna bas sgra thos pa'i dus su /
NK126(cho)003:572: 'o na spro bsdu byas kyang mi lto /
NK126(cho)003:573: rang lugs kyi thig le las ma 'das /
NK126(cho)003:579: ci byas thams cad byang chub sems thig le nyag cig las 'da' ye /
NK126(cho)003:580: thig le la phyogs cha yod dam /
NK126(cho)003:581: ye shes zang thal du mi 'dug gam /
NK126(cho)003:582: des na phyad pa chen po /
NK126(cho)003:585: gzhi bzhag chen po la 'di ltar yin /
NK126(cho)003:586: ci ltar min pa ci 'dug go //
NK126(cho)003:587: phyogs med rgya yan chen po la /
NK126(cho)003:588: yin min bya yang lto lags so //
NK126(cho)003:589: rnam cig tu bsgom ma bsgom ci mchis /
NK126(cho)003:591: bdag gzhan thig le nyag cig tu bsal bas chog mod /
NK126(cho)003:594: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la rtogs pa phul ba /
NK126(cho)003:595: bdag gzhan gnyis ni mnyam pa'i ngang /
NK126(cho)003:596: gnyis su 'gyur yang sems la g.yos pa med /
NK126(cho)003:597: e ma ci rtogs thig le mthong ba med pa'i mthong ba cig /
NK126(cho)003:598: gzhan gyis rtogs snyams bdag mi bgyid /
NK126(cho)003:599: ces zer nas slob dpon la brkyang phyag lan stong du 'tshal lo //
NK126(cho)003:600: der slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che dgyes nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:601: rgen mo khyod ni ye shes sgron ma zhig 'dug go //
NK126(cho)003:603: ru sangs rgyas dbus gtsang na byon pa'i lo rgyus ni /
NK126(cho)003:604: khengs log gi 'khrugs pa'i dbus nas bston nas /
NK126(cho)003:605: snyen mo bya mkhar du byon no //
NK126(cho)003:608: sras lnga yod pa'i tshig cig bsad skad /
NK126(cho)003:609: de nas sras kyi mgo mthu khud du bcug nas bshags pa mdzad /
NK126(cho)003:610: bu kun la 'khrug pa ma byed byas pas nyams su ma 'dod nas /
NK126(cho)003:612: rang gi rdzang lhud mo la gter du sbas /
NK126(cho)003:613: zab pa rnams stag sgro gzig sgror bcug nas /
NK126(cho)003:614: bang bu ga ba zhig la bkal nas /
NK126(cho)003:615: la btsas rtsa nas yar byon pas /
NK126(cho)003:617: g.yas ban ma bon zhing rmo ba'i gan du phyin nas ngal bsos pas /
NK126(cho)003:618: ban ma bon gyi jo bo gang nas 'ong byas nas /
NK126(cho)003:619: nga dbus yul rang nas 'ong gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:620: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes bya ba sgra chen de ngo shes sam byas pas /
NK126(cho)003:624: zla ba 'ga' bdag gis chos ston drang gi bzhugs gnas pas /
NK126(cho)003:625: gar skyid pha yul yin bsdad gsungs nas /
NK126(cho)003:626: bya lung gi brtag gi dben par bzhugs so //
NK126(cho)003:628: yon tan rgya mtsho la ma gshin bshad /
NK126(cho)003:629: so la sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad dang /
NK126(cho)003:630: sems phyogs bsgrub pa rnam gsum bshad /
NK126(cho)003:631: sru legs pa'i sgron ma la bdud rtsi bshad /
NK126(cho)003:632: pa gor la sems phyogs dkar po bshad /
NK126(cho)003:634: snye nams na mar tshol du phyin pa'i dus su /
NK126(cho)003:635: ru bsnyung nad kyis thebs nas bkar shog rgya bo che /
NK126(cho)003:637: ma gshin bcug pa'i po ti /
NK126(cho)003:639: dngul gyi spar khab tu bcug pa zhig gnub rje 'bangs kyi kha lo bsgyur bas /
NK126(cho)003:640: mthu 'di dgos snyoms nas so ye shes dbang phyug la gtad nas /
NK126(cho)003:641: khyod kyis 'di la ma blta bar yon tan rgya mtsho kho la gtod gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:642: lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis la sku drongs te /
NK126(cho)003:643: spur rang gi yul du spyan 'dren pa la /
NK126(cho)003:644: nam mkha' bya bye'u mang po 'dus nas /
NK126(cho)003:645: spur la bsil bsgrib byas nas 'bu tsho stong du bskyal /
NK126(cho)003:646: thab stag gi bya bye'u g.yung du bskyal /
NK126(cho)003:647: spur sbyongs bas bya bye'u tsho gyes so //
NK126(cho)003:649: gnub sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches /
NK126(cho)003:650: rgan mo skye tsha la shel brag tu rgan mo mdzub tshugs su gsungs pa'i skabs te bzhi pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:651: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:652: sems ni rgyu las ma byung /
NK126(cho)003:654: rkyen gyis mi 'gyur nam mkha'i ngo bo 'dra /
NK126(cho)003:655: bya brtsal med do ye nas sangs rgyas yin /
NK126(cho)003:657: gnub pad+ma dbang rgyal gyis zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:658: sems la rang bzhin med pa skye med chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)003:659: sems ni cir yang snang ba thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)003:660: sems ni snang stong dbyer med longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)003:661: sems ni gang shar byas kyang sku gsum lhun gyis grub /
NK126(cho)003:662: ci ltar bsam yang bade'o chos nyid klong du bde //
NK126(cho)003:664: pa gor blon chen 'phags kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:665: sems ni cis kyang mtshon du ma btub chos kyi sku //
NK126(cho)003:666: dran rig cir yang snang ba thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK126(cho)003:667: mtshon du med pa'i dran rig 'di //
NK126(cho)003:668: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes bya //
NK126(cho)003:669: dgag bsgrub med pa gang ltar khyer yang bde //
NK126(cho)003:670: re dogs med pas 'khor bar thar nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:672: sru legs pa'i sgron ma'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:673: skye ba med pas 'khor bar skyes kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:674: 'gags pa med pas bsgom du byas kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:675: lhun grub chen po 'dug pas re dogs kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:676: bya bral chen por 'dug pas bya byed byas kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:677: ye nas sangs rgyas su 'dug pas bsgom bsgrub ma byas kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:678: a ti rang sems rtogs na gang ltar byas kyang bde /
NK126(cho)003:681: skal ldan kun kyang chos sku ma tshol rang sems byar med tshol /
NK126(cho)003:682: sprul sku ma blta rang sems 'gyur byed dran pa ltos /
NK126(cho)003:683: longs sku ma blta rang sems lhun grub ltos /
NK126(cho)003:684: a ti rang sems mthong bas sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /
NK126(cho)003:686: so ye shes dbang phyug zhal nas 'di skad gsungs phyogs cig ma lhung /
NK126(cho)003:687: rang gi sems nyid rang byung ye shes chen po yin /
NK126(cho)003:688: 'di ni sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /'di ni cis
NK126(cho)003:689: kyang ma bsgrubs lam chen kun gyi mchog /'di ni
NK126(cho)003:690: lta bas mi mthong shes mi nus /
NK126(cho)003:691: rtogs pas yang ni shin tu dka'/
NK126(cho)003:692: dbang po phra ba'i theg dman gyis //
NK126(cho)003:693: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob 'dod de //
NK126(cho)003:694: sems can sangs rgyas yin par ma shes pas //
NK126(cho)003:695: bla med sangs rgyas rnyed pa shin du dka' //
NK126(cho)003:696: a ti rang sems rtogs pa sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /
NK126(cho)003:697: de la sangs rgyas gzhan las ma tshol cig /
NK126(cho)003:699: dan yon tan mchog gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:700: a ti rang sems de nyid mi g.yo nam mkha' 'dra /
NK126(cho)003:701: g.yo rdul tha snyad ci snyed pa //
NK126(cho)003:702: mi rtog ye shes rgya mtsho che //
NK126(cho)003:703: 'di ni rang byung lhun grub dkyil 'khor yin //
NK126(cho)003:704: 'bad rtsol bya rgyu ngas ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)003:707: snang srid 'khor ba kha brgyud kyang //
NK126(cho)003:708: snying po dbyings la gar ma phyin //
NK126(cho)003:709: mtha' dbus med pa'i zhing bsgrod kyang //
NK126(cho)003:710: snying po de las g.yos pa med //
NK126(cho)003:711: dpag med rgyal ba'i sku 'khrungs kyang //
NK126(cho)003:712: snying po yongs su 'pho ba med //
NK126(cho)003:713: sems can mthar thug med byung yang //
NK126(cho)003:714: de nyid de las sgrib pa med //
NK126(cho)003:715: rang sems rtogs pas rtsal dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:717: dan yon tan mchog gi sras /
NK126(cho)003:718: slob dpon chen po g+hu ya tsan+t+ra de ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs so //
NK126(cho)003:719: sems nyid a ti rdzogs chen 'di //
NK126(cho)003:720: snang stong phyogs su ma lhung dbyer med rgya yan yin //
NK126(cho)003:721: 'khor 'das phyogs gcig ma lhung bya bral rgya yan yin //
NK126(cho)003:722: yin min gnyis dang bral bas 'dzin med rgya yan yin //
NK126(cho)003:723: 'bad rtsol bya rgyu ngas ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)003:725: ngab thung ye shes kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:726: phyi nang chos rnams ci snyed rtsad bcad pas /
NK126(cho)003:727: chos rnams shes par bya ba'i sems su med //
NK126(cho)003:728: sems kyi ngo bo 'di 'dra su la yang bstan du yang ngas ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)003:729: bstan du med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK126(cho)003:730: bya brtsal med pa'i chos skur 'dug /
NK126(cho)003:731: yid ches thag chod blo gcig bde //
NK126(cho)003:732: 'jal gyi nyal nas las rnams zin nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:734: ngab thung byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:735: sems dang yi dam lha ru dbyer du med //
NK126(cho)003:736: dbyer med chos sku gsal la ma chags na //
NK126(cho)003:737: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob bo dgongs //
NK126(cho)003:739: rtogs rog po tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyi 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:740: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni //
NK126(cho)003:741: rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis la grol //
NK126(cho)003:742: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis la grol //
NK126(cho)003:743: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis las grol nas gada'o //
NK126(cho)003:744: re dogs gnyis po rlung gi khyer //
NK126(cho)003:745: bya rgyu chen po ngas ma rnyed //
NK126(cho)003:747: skor thung shes rab grags kyi zhal nas gsungs pa /
NK126(cho)003:748: sems ni ngo bo med pa kun la khyab //
NK126(cho)003:749: btsal na med la bzhag na 'tshar //
NK126(cho)003:750: 'di ni sus kyang mi shes kyang //
NK126(cho)003:751: mtshon du ma btub cig kyang med //
NK126(cho)003:753: sus kyang shes par mi nus te //
NK126(cho)003:754: de nyid sangs rgyas yin par shes //
NK126(cho)003:755: byar med lhug par gar dga' stabs bde chog /
NK126(cho)003:757: spang mi pham mgon po'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:758: yang dag nges pa'i lung chen 'di //
NK126(cho)003:759: gang las ma byung rig pa rang las byung //
NK126(cho)003:760: sus kyang ma byas ye nas rang byung yin //
NK126(cho)003:761: gang la'ang mi skye nam mkha' lta bu'i sku //
NK126(cho)003:763: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:764: ci yang dgag bsgrub med na sems nyid rtogs pa yin /
NK126(cho)003:765: gang la 'dzin chags med na bla med rnyed pa yin /
NK126(cho)003:766: su yang mchod du med na lha rnams 'grub pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:767: ngag tu bzlas brjod med na snying po rdzogs pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:768: ci yang bsgrub tu med na dngos grub thob pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:770: rje btsun byar med sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:771: ma bcos bde ba'i klong du 'khor ba ye nas bcom /
NK126(cho)003:772: mnyams pa chos las tshig gi mtha' las 'das //
NK126(cho)003:773: kun tu ma bsgrib chos nyid klong du gsal //
NK126(cho)003:774: sus kyang ma bstan rig pa rang shar yin //
NK126(cho)003:775: 'di la rtsol zhing bsgrub pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:776: tshi chad pa yin gyis zin //
NK126(cho)003:778: bla ma phyogs med rgya yan gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:779: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo a ti sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)003:780: sems ni 'khor 'das yangs kyi snying po ste //
NK126(cho)003:781: gang yang mi 'byed dbyer med chen po yin nam snyams //
NK126(cho)003:782: gang zhig so sor dgag bsgrub byed //
NK126(cho)003:783: nges pa'i don la gol te blang dor mtha' la ltung //
NK126(cho)003:784: mnyams pa chen po rtogs na 'khor ba'i nad las thar gda'/
NK126(cho)003:785: me dkar gyi sum pa dbang tshul gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:786: bslab kyin bslab kyin slob gnyer sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:787: bltas kyin bltas kyin rtogs pa sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:788: bsgoms kyin bsgoms kyin bsgom pa sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:789: bsgrub kyin bsgrub kyin 'bras bu sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:790: phyi ru snang ba bltas pas bzungs ba sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:791: nang du sems la bltas pas 'dzin mkhan sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:792: gsang ba dgongs ltas pas chos sku sangs nas thal //
NK126(cho)003:793: phyi sangs nang sangs dbyer ru med par sangs //
NK126(cho)003:794: sangs ba nyid na rang snang cir yang ma dgags rgyas //
NK126(cho)003:795: sangs rgyas dbyer med bde chen bya rtsal med //
NK126(cho)003:796: da ni blo rgya nyal bas chog par gda' //
NK126(cho)003:798: dkar ston shes rab 'bar ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:799: snang srid 'khor 'das chos kyi sku nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:800: su yis bcos kyang 'di la bsgrub tu med //
NK126(cho)003:801: su yis bslad kyang 'di la dngos po mtshan ma med //
NK126(cho)003:802: 'gyur ba med pa'i bag nag bzhin //
NK126(cho)003:803: chos sku rang gi sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)003:804: bya brtsal med par lhun grub chen por yin //
NK126(cho)003:805: blang dor med do ri dwags rgya nas thar nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:807: me nyag shes rab gsal ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:808: skye med rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK126(cho)003:809: dge sdig gnyis kyi 'bras bu med //
NK126(cho)003:810: sa bon med pa 'bras bu ga la smin //
NK126(cho)003:811: de phyir skye ba med ces bya //
NK126(cho)003:812: cir yang snang ba rang snang yin //
NK126(cho)003:813: des na ci snang rang byung ye shes yin //
NK126(cho)003:814: des na gsal bar bsgom pas ngan song 'gro re kan //
NK126(cho)003:816: me nyag 'byung drag gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:817: skye med sems kyi ngo bo 'di //
NK126(cho)003:818: khyab brdal nam mkha'i rang bzhin te /
NK126(cho)003:819: dran tshad shar tshad rig tshad skyes tshad chos sku rig pa zang thal yin /
NK126(cho)003:820: dgag bsgrub med do de nyid zang thal yin /
NK126(cho)003:821: spang blang med do de nyid zang thal yin /
NK126(cho)003:822: re dogs med do de nyid zang thal yin /
NK126(cho)003:823: zang thal chen po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:825: myang ye shes mchog gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:826: sems ni gang yang ma yin pas /
NK126(cho)003:827: nga la 'dod pa gang yang med //
NK126(cho)003:829: myang ye shes 'byung gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:830: sems kyi rtsa ba bcad pas stor nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:831: chos kyi rtsa ba bcad pas zad nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:832: dgongs pa'i mthar thug mtshon pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:834: rong pa chos bzang gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:835: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba ni /
NK126(cho)003:836: lam rnams gang yang bkag pa med //
NK126(cho)003:837: a ti rang sems ma rtogs na //
NK126(cho)003:839: bcings grol med pa'i chos sku rang gi sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)003:841: glan sh+aakya byang chub kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:842: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)003:843: byang chub sems la sku yi mtshan ma med //
NK126(cho)003:845: byang chub sems la tshig med mtshon pa'i tshig dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:846: byang chub sems la thug med chags pa'i gnas dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:847: sangs rgyas dgongs pa sku gsung thugs dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:849: glan sh+aakya bzang po'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:850: med par 'dod na log rtogs nyon mongs med par 'dod kyang chad lta yin /
NK126(cho)003:851: yod par 'dod na yi dam lha la yod par 'dod kyang rtag lta yin /
NK126(cho)003:852: spang par 'dod na 'tshams med lnga po spang bar 'dod kyang rang sems mnyam nyid ma rtogs skyon /
NK126(cho)003:853: sgrub cing spang blang mthong na kun dang dgongs pa
NK126(cho)003:854: blang byar mthong yang rang sems mnyam nyid ma mthong
NK126(cho)003:857: bsgom na gnyis su med par bsgom yang 'ching /
NK126(cho)003:858: mthong bar 'dod na yi dam lha'i zhal mthong yang 'khrul pa yin /
NK126(cho)003:859: ye sangs rgyas pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK126(cho)003:860: re dogs spang blang gang yang med //
NK126(cho)003:862: gro gtsug tor gzhon nu'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:863: skye med sems kyi ngo bo 'di /
NK126(cho)003:864: de las 'das pa'i mtshan ma'i ngo bo med //
NK126(cho)003:865: tshig las 'das pas brjod pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:866: sgra las 'das pas thob pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:867: kha dog med pas gsal 'grib yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:868: ci yang med pas phan gnod med //
NK126(cho)003:869: nam mkha' lta bur bcod pa'i yul med do //
NK126(cho)003:871: zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:872: wa yis seng+gera bcos nas skad phyungs kyang /
NK126(cho)003:873: seng+gera mi 'gyur rang nyid sgying bar ltar //
NK126(cho)003:875: ji ltar brjod kyang de nyid min //
NK126(cho)003:876: phyogs med blang dor med pa de //
NK126(cho)003:877: blo yis myang ba byar med par //
NK126(cho)003:879: 'di rnams phyir mi ldog pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NK126(cho)003:881: me nyag ston pa'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:882: skye med sems kyi ngo bo 'di //
NK126(cho)003:883: ye sangs rgyas pas 'phel dang 'grib pa med //
NK126(cho)003:884: lta ba'i mchog ni cir yang lta rgyu med //
NK126(cho)003:885: bsgom pa'i rgyal po gang la'ang dmigs gtad med //
NK126(cho)003:886: spyod pa'i rgyal po bzang ngan gnyis dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:887: 'bras bu'i rgyal po ye nas skye med yin //
NK126(cho)003:889: me nyag bya tsha'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:890: theg pa'i theg pa rang byung ye shes che //
NK126(cho)003:891: 'khor 'das gnyis 'byung sems nyid rin po che //
NK126(cho)003:892: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pa'i don po che //
NK126(cho)003:893: snang srid ma lus khyab pa'i rgya bo che //
NK126(cho)003:894: 'khor 'das dus gcig rdzogs pa'i dbang po che //
NK126(cho)003:895: sa lam rim par ma sbyangs 'tshangs po che //
NK126(cho)003:896: rgyud drug dong sprug yongs rdzogs stobs po che //
NK126(cho)003:897: nyon mongs chos skur grol ba'i mthu bo che //
NK126(cho)003:898: khams gsum dus cig 'joms pa'i rtsal po che //
NK126(cho)003:899: gang la rag ma lus pa'i mnga' bo che //
NK126(cho)003:900: de ltar rang sems rtsol sgrub yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:902: zhes bsod nams bzang po'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:903: snang srid thig le chen por sangs rgyas pas //
NK126(cho)003:904: spang blang 'dug par ngas ma mthong //
NK126(cho)003:905: mnyam pa chen po'i sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:906: bsgrod rgyu 'dug par ngas ma mthong //
NK126(cho)003:907: skye med mkha' ltar dag pa las //
NK126(cho)003:908: bsgrub rgyu 'dug par ngas ma mthong //
NK126(cho)003:910: za na khyi smyon bzhin du za //
NK126(cho)003:911: nyal na khyi smyon bzhin du nyal //
NK126(cho)003:912: blo mi bde ma mchis bde mor mchis //
NK126(cho)003:914: mar pa sh+aaka tshul gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:915: rang gi rig pa'i sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:916: ngas ci tsam bltas pas ci yang ma mthong na /
NK126(cho)003:917: sangs rgyas sems can la sogs pa //
NK126(cho)003:918: 'di tsam ming cig rnyed pa ci //
NK126(cho)003:919: chos dang chos min su yis 'byed //
NK126(cho)003:920: bde sdug gnyis ka byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)003:921: sems la bde sdug dbye ru med //
NK126(cho)003:922: dper na nam mkha' stong pa la //
NK126(cho)003:923: nyid dang mtshan nyid dbyer med dam //
NK126(cho)003:925: mar pa dbyig tshul gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:926: rgyud drug sems can thams cad kun //
NK126(cho)003:927: sus kyang byas med byed mi 'gyur //
NK126(cho)003:928: rgyu rkyen gnyis las ma byung bas //
NK126(cho)003:929: nam mkha' bzhin du ye sangs rgyas //
NK126(cho)003:933: dge bshes g.yu'i lhun po'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:934: sems la bde sdug dran rig ci snang yang //
NK126(cho)003:935: rang byung ye shes rgyal po yin //
NK126(cho)003:936: rang byung ye shes rgyal po 'di //
NK126(cho)003:937: sangs rgyas nang nas rje btsan yin //
NK126(cho)003:938: ci phyir skye shi med pa'i nam mkha' yin //
NK126(cho)003:940: bsgrub pa rtsol sgrub med pa yin //
NK126(cho)003:941: sangs rgyas ye shes chos sku yin //
NK126(cho)003:943: snyan dbang drag gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:944: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK126(cho)003:945: nam mkha' 'dra bas bcos su med //
NK126(cho)003:947: des na rtsol med chen por nyal //
NK126(cho)003:949: zur dbang phyug rgyal mtshan gyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:950: bsgom pa bsam gtan yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:951: spyod pa blang dor yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:952: lta ba 'dod pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:953: 'bras bu bsgrub rgyu yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:954: nan ltar bltas pas chos med po zhig 'dug /
NK126(cho)003:956: rngog byang chub rdo rje'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:957: rtogs na rtogs rgyu ci yang med //
NK126(cho)003:958: bsgom na bsgom rgyu ci yang med //
NK126(cho)003:959: spyad na spyad pa 'di yin med //
NK126(cho)003:960: 'bras bu thob rgyu gang yang med //
NK126(cho)003:961: re dogs med pa'i blo 'di ni //
NK126(cho)003:962: mkha' la khyung chen lding ba 'dra //
NK126(cho)003:963: nyams nga med pa'i rtsal chen seng ge 'dra //
NK126(cho)003:964: rtsol ba med pa'i gding chen nga la yod //
NK126(cho)003:966: ldan ma tshul khrims kyi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:968: sems nyid rang snang yin pa na //
NK126(cho)003:969: thams cad dgag bsgrub med do mnyam pa nyid //
NK126(cho)003:970: 'di zhes mtshon pa'i yul dang bral //
NK126(cho)003:972: sle bo mchog 'byung gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:973: rang sems ma rtogs bskal pa'i chos la zad mtha' med //
NK126(cho)003:974: rang sems rtogs pas chos la bya rgyu med //
NK126(cho)003:975: 'di zhes da la bstan du med //
NK126(cho)003:977: g.yu blo gros rgyal ba'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:978: rtogs pas rtogs pa'i blo dang grol //
NK126(cho)003:979: bsgom pas bsgom pa'i blo las grol //
NK126(cho)003:980: spyod pas blang dor blo las grol //
NK126(cho)003:981: 'bras bu thob pa'i rtogs pa bral //
NK126(cho)003:982: bshad pas tshig gi na ya stor //
NK126(cho)003:983: mkhas pas blo sbyangs ci dgar mdzod //
NK126(cho)003:985: lce ye shes sh+aakya'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:986: nyon mongs rtsa ba bcad pa'i sems su gda' //
NK126(cho)003:987: sems kyi rtsa ba bcad pas mtha' med rlung gis khyer //
NK126(cho)003:988: chos rnams rtsa ba bcad pas sems su gda' //
NK126(cho)003:989: sems kyi rtsa ba bcad pas stor na gda' //
NK126(cho)003:990: 'khor 'das gnyis ka rang gi sems nyid la //
NK126(cho)003:991: sems kyi rtsa ba bcad pas 'khor 'das gnyis ka song //
NK126(cho)003:992: de rtogs pas skye med nam mkha' bzhin du rgyas //
NK126(cho)003:993: sangs rgyas zer na nga la gyis //
NK126(cho)003:995: snyan lha po'i zhal nas 'di skad gsungs //
NK126(cho)003:996: a ti rang gi sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)003:997: gnyen pos bcos su med de bya bral nyid la snang ba med //
NK126(cho)003:998: 'di yin 'di man rgyal ba nyid kyis gsungs pa med //
NK126(cho)003:1000: sum pa blo rgyal gyis zur chung la /
NK126(cho)003:1001: zur chung khyed dgongs pa'i mthar thug cug byed zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:1003: kho bo ci'i mngon zhen mi gda' //
NK126(cho)003:1005: be lung gi ba gog bya tshal zur chung la khyed kyi sems nyid cug go zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:1007: snang ba ci yang snang ste /
NK126(cho)003:1008: zhen ci yang ma zhen pas /
NK126(cho)003:1009: phyogs gcig pa'i gza' gtad bral //
NK126(cho)003:1013: rtsol bral chos kyi sku ru ye nas gda' //
NK126(cho)003:1017: khyed kyi a ti rdzogs chen 'di //
NK126(cho)003:1018: go lug cug go zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:1019: zur chung gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:1020: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams byang chub sems su go //
NK126(cho)003:1021: byang chub sems ni dbyer med lhun gyis grub //
NK126(cho)003:1022: gser gling phyin pa 'dra ste nyon mongs ye shes blang dor med par go //
NK126(cho)003:1023: rgyu 'bras med de gzhi lam ye sangs rgyas su 'dug /
NK126(cho)003:1024: sa bdag rgyal po ni spyan gyis gzigs pas //
NK126(cho)003:1025: yul 'khor thams cad bran g.yog min pa med pa bzhin //
NK126(cho)003:1026: 'khor 'das gzhi bzhengs chos sku yin par go //
NK126(cho)003:1027: des na thams cad bya bral yin //
NK126(cho)003:1028: bya ba btang ba'i skyes bu dang 'dra ste byang chub brtsal ba med par go //
NK126(cho)003:1029: des na rang grol du 'dug pas skyes bu gnyid sad pa dang 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)003:1030: 'khor 'das bzang ngan gnyis dang bral bar go //
NK126(cho)003:1031: des na lta ba phyogs med nam mkha' 'dra ste /
NK126(cho)003:1032: dgongs pa'i yul las 'das par go //
NK126(cho)003:1033: man ngag gser la nag mtshur btang ba dang 'dra ste car phog dang rjen cer du go //
NK126(cho)003:1035: tre byang chub rgyal ba'i zur chung la /
NK126(cho)003:1036: byang chub sems ni ji ltar lags zhus pas /
NK126(cho)003:1038: rgyu rkyen gnyis dang bral bas rtsol sgrub byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)003:1039: gzhi nas ye sangs rgyas pas kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)003:1040: ya mtshan tshig las 'das pas chos sku byang chub sems //
NK126(cho)003:1041: thams cad lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs chen lhun grub yin //
NK126(cho)003:1043: zur chung gi zhal nas 'di skad gsungs /
NK126(cho)003:1044: a ti rang gi sems nyid 'di //
NK126(cho)003:1045: ci yang dmigs su med de gang yang dmigs su mi byed do //
NK126(cho)003:1048: bka' brgyud bla ma'i bcud phyungs nas man ngag rtogs pa'i nyams kyi thig pa zag pa /
NK126(cho)003:1049: dgongs pa'i nyams rin po che'i phreng ba ltar du gsungs pa'i skabs te lnga pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:1050: zur chung shes rab grags pas span phug tu dgongs
NK126(cho)003:1051: pa'i mthar thug tu yig bshad mtshams brgyad pa 'di
NK126(cho)003:1053: bla dbye kha ru bzhag pas /
NK126(cho)003:1054: kun gyis bltas shing gzigs nas /
NK126(cho)003:1055: phyag 'tshal zhing spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK126(cho)003:1056: lta dgongs kyi rtse mor gyur pa zur chung shes rab grags pa kun gyis bsgrags so //
NK126(cho)003:1057: zur chung shes rab grags pa 'di sprul pa'i sku
NK126(cho)003:1058: mkhas pa phul du phyin pa de yin nges so
NK126(cho)003:1059: // yul gyi dngos po sems nyid skye ba med //
NK126(cho)003:1060: gnas kyi mchog tu ting 'dzin yongs na bde //
NK126(cho)003:1061: rang rig pa'i mthar thug tu /
NK126(cho)003:1062: rnal 'byor bdag gi dam tshig rnam grangs bral /
NK126(cho)003:1064: chos kyi dbyings nyid rang bzhin ma bcos gnas //
NK126(cho)003:1065: de la rnal 'byor tshad ma nga yis bsten /
NK126(cho)003:1066: slob ma'i dus su bya byed don mi dmigs //
NK126(cho)003:1068: dam pa'i don du mtshon cing brtags par dka' //
NK126(cho)003:1069: dam pa'i gdams ngag yul du bsam du bral //
NK126(cho)003:1071: dam pa'i tha tshig bsrung ba'i phyogs ris bral //
NK126(cho)003:1072: dam pa'i spyod pa ma 'gags ci bder gnas //
NK126(cho)003:1073: ma yin dam pa snying rje kun khyab gdal //
NK126(cho)003:1075: mtha'/ g.yas phyogs mtho dman ci yang snang //
NK126(cho)003:1077: rgya dang bral bas sems nyid nam mkha' 'dra //
NK126(cho)003:1079: lha mchog dngos po thig le nyag cig yin //
NK126(cho)003:1081: rtsol ba'i spyod pa rnam dag rlung mi bzlog /
NK126(cho)003:1082: dam tshig rgyal ba'i thugs dang 'dra rnam ni //
NK126(cho)003:1084: rgyu gnyis bzhin du so sor gyes pa med //
NK126(cho)003:1086: tsit+ta'i mkha' klong yongs pa'i klong //
NK126(cho)003:1088: btsun bsrung med dam tshig sdom pa rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:1089: bral dang ma bral dbyings la dbye rgyu med //
NK126(cho)003:1090: gzhung ldan spyod pas phrin las ma bkag pas //
NK126(cho)003:1091: thag pa sbrul bzhin 'khrul pa'i rang bzhin gnas //
NK126(cho)003:1092: dge sdig las kyis bsam zhing bsgrib tu med //
NK126(cho)003:1093: shes rab bya ba rang gi sems nyid yin //
NK126(cho)003:1094: spyod pa mtha' bral du bstan /
NK126(cho)003:1095: nges pa'i don la spyod pa 'dzin chags med //
NK126(cho)003:1096: 'dzin rtog mi bral gang yang dbye ba med //
NK126(cho)003:1097: lung du ma bstan lta ba bza' btad bral //
NK126(cho)003:1099: sus kyang bya ba med de bsgom pa'i klong chen yin //
NK126(cho)003:1100: grags pa'i chos brgyad mkhas pa'i bslab bya min //
NK126(cho)003:1101: longs med spyod pa rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal yin //
NK126(cho)003:1102: phrin las mtha' bral du bstan /
NK126(cho)003:1103: yin pa med pas lta ba spangs shing bsgrub tu med //
NK126(cho)003:1104: bsgrub tu med pa'i chos 'byung ye nas gnas //
NK126(cho)003:1105: rtogs pa 'di lta ba'i gol sa gcod /
NK126(cho)003:1106: yul med 'khrul pa shes mi nus //
NK126(cho)003:1107: lta ba 'di med gzung 'dzin mtha' mi grol //
NK126(cho)003:1108: med pa 'bras bu gzhan du tshol bas 'khrul //
NK126(cho)003:1109: 'di ting nge 'dzin gyi gol sa gcod /
NK126(cho)003:1110: bsgom pa'i tshe na ci yang dmigs su med //
NK126(cho)003:1111: ting 'dzin 'di min gnyen po'i rlung mi ldog /
NK126(cho)003:1112: lhun grub ngang la 'khor ba spang du med //
NK126(cho)003:1114: rtsol bsgrub dka' ba spyod pa ci bzhin bsrungs //
NK126(cho)003:1115: spyod pa 'di min rtsol bsgrub nad mi thar //
NK126(cho)003:1116: 'dis dam tshig gis gol sa gcod /
NK126(cho)003:1117: rdzogs chen bya bral chos sku 'gyur ba med //
NK126(cho)003:1118: mkhas pas sdom zhing rigs su bsrungs du med //
NK126(cho)003:1119: dam tshig 'di min dka' thub mdud mi grol //
NK126(cho)003:1120: sa nyid bsgrod du med pas sgrib pa sbyangs su med //
NK126(cho)003:1121: phrin las 'di min bdag gzhan don mi rdzogs //
NK126(cho)003:1122: ye nas gnon pas da dgongs rtsol mi dgos //
NK126(cho)003:1123: kun gyi rang bzhin 'dis dbang gis gol sa gcod /
NK126(cho)003:1125: 'bras bu rdzogs chen a ti'i 'khor 'das kyi chos bzang ngan rtsol sgrub kyi mtha' las 'das nas gda'/
NK126(cho)003:1127: snying 'dis snying rje'i gol sa gcod /
NK126(cho)003:1128: rje yul las gdung pa skye ba med //
NK126(cho)003:1130: lha rje zur chung ba bod kyi lta dgongs kyi rtse mor gyur pa de /
NK126(cho)003:1131: btu yig bshad mtshams brgyad pa dgongs pa'i mthar thug
NK126(cho)003:1132: pa'i span phug tu mdzad nas bla dbye'i kha ru
NK126(cho)003:1133: bzhugs su bcug pa'i skabs te drug pa'o //
NK126(cho)003:1136: sems phyogs kyi dbang mo che mdzad dus su /
NK126(cho)003:1137: 'dra 'bags chen mo 'di zhang mkhar gsal bas bla ma la bka' zhus nas /
NK126(cho)003:1138: thugs la btags nas gnang ngo //
NK126(cho)003:1140: bod kyi bla ma rnams kyi dgongs pa'i nyams rin
